en Zukunft ausrichten. Diese Geisteswissenschaften stellen sich in den Dienst allen Lebens auf unserem Planeten und sind dadurch in der Lage, neu formulierte, verbindliche Werte in die Gesellschaft hineinzutragen und der Zerstörung unserer Umwelt entschlossen entgegenzutreten.  afunded by THE NEW INSTITUTE  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-SA 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 4aDenken. 4aGesellschaft. 4aHandeln. 4aKrise. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aLeben. 4aNatur. 4aSoziologie. 4aUmwelt. 4aUmweltethik. 4aWandel. 4aWert. 4aWissenschaft. 4aZukunft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aActing.  aChange.  aCrisis.  aCultural Studies.  aEnvironment.  aEnvironmental Ethics.  aFuture.  aLife.  aNature.  aScience.  aSociety.  aSociology.  aThought.  aValue.1 aHorn, Christoph, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKatsman, Anna, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aLippold, Anna Luisa, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aMilles, Joachim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPelluchon, Corine, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aVenzke, Ingo, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut2 aTHE NEW INSTITUTEefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022z9783110993738oZDB-23-DKU40